Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.16,0:00:03.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rick 在这个宇宙飞船里\N{\fs38}I got to tell you, Rick. It's pretty great
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.94,0:00:05.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就我们两人 真是挺好的\N{\fs38}To be in this spaceship, just the two of us, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.97,0:00:07.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就到处这样游荡 这风格才对嘛\N{\fs38}Just cruising around, Rick and Morty style.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.80,0:00:09.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我同意 Morty\N{\fs38}I agree, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.05,0:00:10.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样返璞归真挺好的\N{\fs38}It's nice to get back to the basics
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.26,0:00:12.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经过了过去紧张的 混乱的一年\N{\fs38}After a pretty intense, mixed-bag of a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.68,0:00:13.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 哦  - 放松\N{\fs38}- Ohh!  - Relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.70,0:00:15.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挡风玻璃就是干这个用的\N{\fs38}That's what windshields are for.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.10,0:00:16.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都不知道太空里还有虫子呢\N{\fs38}I didn't know that there were bugs out in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.90,0:00:18.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 那你怎么想的 Morty\N{\fs38}Well, w-what did you think, Morty?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.46,0:00:20.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生命难道是地球自己进化出来的\N{\fs38}Life just developed on earth by itself?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.32,0:00:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我处理处理\N{\fs38}Here, let me take care of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.00,0:00:25.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天呐 Rick 真恶心\N{\fs38}Geez, Rick, that's disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.18,0:00:26.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想看\N{\fs38}I don't want to look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.18,0:00:27.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像没有清洁液了\N{\fs38}Yeah, guess I'm out of fluid.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.52,0:00:29.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我找个地方停一下\N{\fs38}L-let me find a place to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.26,0:00:36.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 你们星球有擦挡风玻璃的清洁液吗\N{\fs38}Hey, muchacho, does your planet have wiper fluid yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.68,0:00:38.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说你们已经吓傻了要把我们当神拜了\N{\fs38}Or are you gonna freak out and start worshipping us?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.56,0:00:41.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 杂货店里应该有你要的东西  - 谢谢\N{\fs38}- The general store ought to have what you need. - Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.20,0:00:43.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你肯定想要在日落前离开这里\N{\fs38}Of course, you'll be wanting to be gone from here by sundown.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.94,0:00:46.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 当然 等一下 什么 为什么啊\N{\fs38}Yeah, sure thing. Wait a minute. What? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.20,0:00:48.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日落以后节日就开始了\N{\fs38}Sundown is when the festival begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.26,0:00:49.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,节日\N{\fs38}The festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.34,0:00:51.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦哦哦 好吧 对于我们Millennia人来说\N{\fs38}Ooh, well, for Millennia,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.90,0:00:54.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的社会已经完全没有犯罪和战争了\N{\fs38}Our society has been free of crime and war,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.82,0:00:57.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我们生活在和平之中  - 哦 我知道这是什么了\N{\fs38}- Living in perfect peace.  - Oh, I know what this is!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.34,0:00:58.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们维持世界和平\N{\fs38}You've been able to sustain world peace
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.90,0:01:01.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠的是每年有一天晚上 能到处\N{\fs38}Because you have one night a year where you all run around
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.18,0:01:03.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抢劫杀人 还不用承担任何后果\N{\fs38}Robbing and murdering each other without consequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.20,0:01:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 是这样的  - 什么\N{\fs38}- That's right. - What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.26,0:01:06.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是<人类清除计划>那电影 Morty\N{\fs38}It's like "The purge," Morty. That movie "The purge"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.48,0:01:07.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 你以前来过这里么\N{\fs38}Oh, have you been here before?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.96,0:01:10.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 但是我去过好几个星球都有这样的东西\N{\fs38}No, no, but I've been to a few planets with the same gimmick.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.10,0:01:12.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道么 有时候这事也叫作"大净化"或者"红色时间"\N{\fs38}You know, sometimes it's called "the cleansing" or "the red time".
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.94,0:01:14.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有这么个世界就直接管这叫"杀人夜"\N{\fs38}There was this one world that called it just murder night.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.18,0:01:16.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这 这是个搞大清除的星球\N{\fs38}I-it's a purge planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.64,0:01:18.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们一片和平 然后 他们搞清除\N{\fs38}They're peaceful, and then, you know, they just purge.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.92,0:01:20.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也太可怕了\N{\fs38}T-that's horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.22,0:01:21.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fs38}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.98,0:01:23.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想看看么\N{\fs38}You want to check it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.48,0:01:56.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 你在节日上一般都干什么啊\N{\fs38}So, what do you do during the festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.00,0:01:59.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是把自己锁在屋里 还是出去干点什么呀\N{\fs38}You lock yourself in, or you go out and do some stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.30,0:02:01.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 我干一些很坏很坏的事\N{\fs38}Oh, I do some pretty bad stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.62,0:02:03.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 我估计也是 老爷子\N{\fs38}Oh, I bet you do, old timer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.04,0:02:06.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天呐 Rick 快走吧 太阳快下山了\N{\fs38}Gee— Rick, come on. The sun is setting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.20,0:02:07.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得离开这里啊\N{\fs38}W-we got to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.60,0:02:09.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 好吧 这个玻璃清洗液多少钱\N{\fs38}All right, well, w-what do I owe you for the wiper fluid?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.64,0:02:11.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,免费的 哦 还有\N{\fs38}It's on the house. Oh, and, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.04,0:02:14.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你再拿点糖吧 \N{\fs38}Why— why don't you have some candy bars, as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.50,0:02:16.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 不会吧 你真好\N{\fs38}Oh, no way. That's really nice of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.34,0:02:18.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是个好人 至少现在是\N{\fs38}I'm a nice guy... for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.70,0:02:20.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦哦 这我不怀疑\N{\fs38}Ohh, I don't doubt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.52,0:02:21.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Rick  - 好啦好啦 \N{\fs38}- Rick!  - Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.00,0:02:23.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 节日上好好玩呀 老爷子\N{\fs38}Hey, have a good festival, old timer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.02,0:02:25.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是这么打算的\N{\fs38}I intend to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.40,0:02:29.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rick 快开门\N{\fs38}Rick, unlock it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.70,0:02:30.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就等一下 Morty\N{\fs38}Just a second, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.94,0:02:32.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 快看那夕阳\N{\fs38}Oh, look at that sunset.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.76,0:02:34.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别闹了\N{\fs38}Stop screwing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.24,0:02:38.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 好多了 现在能看清楚了\N{\fs38}There we go. Much better. Now we can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.88,0:02:39.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呵呵\N{\fs38}Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.72,0:02:41.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 Morty\N{\fs38}Hey, you know what, Morty?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.72,0:02:43.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在玻璃已经擦得锃光瓦亮了\N{\fs38}Why don't we christen our squeaky-clean windshield here
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.80,0:02:45.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们正好看看大清楚怎么样\N{\fs38}By watching a little of this purge through it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.76,0:02:47.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 不 你有病么\N{\fs38}What?! No! What is your problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.70,0:02:49.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty 成熟点吧 你要是不想看\N{\fs38}Morty, grow up. If you don't want to watch,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.48,0:02:51.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就别看 但是 你知道 这是我的车\N{\fs38}Don't watch, but, you know, it's my car.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.32,0:02:53.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 你要是告诉你妈\N{\fs38}Also, if you tell your mom about this,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.26,0:02:54.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我就把你给清除了  - 你太差劲了\N{\fs38}- I'll purge you.  - You're the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.90,0:02:57.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个星球也是 你怎么会喜欢这种东西\N{\fs38}And this planet is the worst. How can you be into this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.18,0:02:58.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看这种互相残杀的戏码\N{\fs38}You know, people are gonna kill each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.64,0:03:00.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么 你坐这儿就是想告诉我\N{\fs38}So, what, y-y-you trying to sit here and tell me that
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.16,0:03:02.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有个在线视频\N{\fs38}I-if -- if there's a video online
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.98,0:03:04.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内容是有人被砍头的那种\N{\fs38}With someone getting decapitated,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.26,0:03:05.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 难道你不会点进去看看  - 不\N{\fs38}- You don't click on it?  - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.56,0:03:07.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么啊 为什么我要点进去看啊 你为什么要看啊\N{\fs38}Why— why would I do that? You do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.76,0:03:09.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不看 因为太无聊了\N{\fs38}I don't, because it would bore me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.22,0:03:11.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吃早点的时候才看那种[哔]玩意儿 Morty\N{\fs38}I see [bleep] like that for breakfast, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.06,0:03:12.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你不点进去看 我说就是因为\N{\fs38}But if you don't do it, I say it's because
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.66,0:03:14.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你惧怕你的原始冲动\N{\fs38}You're afraid of your own primal instincts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.40,0:03:15.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你极力压制他们然后\N{\fs38}So you stuff them down and—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.74,0:03:17.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 哦 嘘 嘘 开始了\N{\fs38}OH, OH! Shh. Shh. It's starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.33,0:03:19.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 哦吼吼 开始啦  - 我不看\N{\fs38}- Oh-ho-ho! Here we go.  - I'm not watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.72,0:03:21.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 好 好 你的奖牌已经寄家去了\N{\fs38}Yeah, yeah, yeah, your medal's in the mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.28,0:03:23.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我要离近点看  - 哦 好吧 随便\N{\fs38}- I'm gonna get a closer look. - Oh, okay, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:24.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下就会有人扔石头\N{\fs38}And then someone's gonna throw a rock
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.42,0:03:26.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打中我们的车 然后车子坠毁\N{\fs38}And hit the car and then we're gonna crash
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.10,0:03:27.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我们就困在下面了\N{\fs38}And we're gonna be stuck down there
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.28,0:03:28.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的就都是我们活该了\N{\fs38}And it's gonna be what we deserve.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.40,0:03:35.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 这真是[哔]的互相残杀\N{\fs38}Whoa, they are purging the [bleep] out of each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.76,0:03:37.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦我的天呐\N{\fs38}Oh, my god!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.58,0:03:39.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦[哔]\N{\fs38}Oh [bleep]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.78,0:03:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是 好吧 那真是恶心\N{\fs38}That was— okay, yeah. T-that was gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.86,0:03:45.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我的胃还是没有我的眼睛坚强\N{\fs38}Man, I think my eyes were bigger than my stomach
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.52,0:03:46.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受不太了这个 Morty\N{\fs38}On this one, Morty. Ugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.06,0:03:49.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对杀戮的观赏欲一瞬间就已经满足了\N{\fs38}My appetite for purge-spectating got filled pretty quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.58,0:03:50.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦天呐\N{\fs38}Oh, god.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.54,0:03:56.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离我远点\N{\fs38}Get away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.80,0:03:57.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不 救命\N{\fs38}No! No! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.10,0:03:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快来人救我呀 啊\N{\fs38}Somebody help me! Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:01.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 Morty 咱 咱们走吧\N{\fs38}All right, Morty. L-let's get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.09,0:04:03.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 等一下 我们得下去\N{\fs38}Wait, wait, wait. Hold on. W-we have to go down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.64,0:04:04.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 为什么啊\N{\fs38}What? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.94,0:04:07.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个可怜的女孩子 我们得救她\N{\fs38}That poor girl. W-we have to save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.38,0:04:09.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 Morty 在宇宙里 有一种东西叫做\N{\fs38}Uh, Morty, in space, we have something we call
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.16,0:04:11.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不干涉原则 我们拿到了玻璃清洗液\N{\fs38}The non-interference policy. We got the wiper fluid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.74,0:04:13.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也看了他们互相残杀 我们要走了\N{\fs38}We watched them kill each other. We're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.62,0:04:16.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我救那个女孩 要不我就告诉我妈你把我带这来了\N{\fs38}Help me save that girl, or I'm telling mom you brought me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.38,0:04:17.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个小贱逼\N{\fs38}You little turd.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.80,0:04:20.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了 放过我吧\N{\fs38}Please! Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.72,0:04:22.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放过你 在大清除上\N{\fs38}Leave you alone? During a purge?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.80,0:04:24.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得不行啊 宝贝\N{\fs38}I don't think so, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.66,0:04:29.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 我们不会伤害你的\N{\fs38}It's okay. We're not gonna hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.52,0:04:31.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫Morty 这是我外公\N{\fs38}My name is Morty. This is my grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.70,0:04:33.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我们是来旅游的  - 不再是了\N{\fs38}- We're tourists.  - Not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.64,0:04:37.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦天呐 这太[哔]爽了\N{\fs38}Oh, my god. This is [bleep] awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.66,0:04:39.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty 这太酷了\N{\fs38}Morty, this is really cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.26,0:04:41.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 你 你想帮我杀几个人不\N{\fs38}Hey, y-you want to help me out here and kill some people?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.00,0:04:43.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好玩的 而且绝对正当\N{\fs38}It's fun. We're totally justified
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:44.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们是为了救一个小女孩啊\N{\fs38}Because we're saving a little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.06,0:04:47.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说 这些人我们可以随便杀 完全没问题\N{\fs38}I mean, w-w-we're both free and clear to murder these people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.94,0:04:49.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你没事吧  - 是的\N{\fs38}- Are you okay?  - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.76,0:04:51.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得找个地方躲一下\N{\fs38}I have to find somewhere to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.14,0:04:52.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 你可以和我们一起啊 Rick\N{\fs38}Well, you can hide with us. Rick?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.04,0:04:54.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 怎么了  - 你觉得我们可以\N{\fs38}- Yeah?  - Do you think we could take—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.82,0:04:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你 你叫什么名字  - Arthrisha\N{\fs38}- W-what's your name?  - Arthrisha.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.36,0:04:58.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以带Arthrisha上车么\N{\fs38}Could we take Arthrisha up in the ship
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.30,0:04:59.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 你懂的 就等着大清除结束\N{\fs38}And, you know, just wait out the purge?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.72,0:05:01.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 Morty 我怎么能拒绝呢\N{\fs38}Oh, Morty, how can I refuse
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.10,0:05:03.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就你刚刚那么威胁过我之后\N{\fs38}After all you've done to blackmail me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.62,0:05:09.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的交通工具 是神赐的么\N{\fs38}Your vehicle— is it from the gods?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.04,0:05:11.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 不  - 是\N{\fs38}-No.  -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.54,0:05:16.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 大清除最开始的时候\N{\fs38}So, uh, you know, when the purge started,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.66,0:05:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家是一下就进入现在这种状态\N{\fs38}Did people get into it right away,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.18,0:05:20.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是 "等等 什么\N{\fs38}Or were they like, "Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.20,0:05:22.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也能阻止犯罪么 到底什么原理啊" 那样的\N{\fs38}This is gonna stop crime how, exactly?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.50,0:05:25.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 最开始人们花了不少时间接受这件事\N{\fs38}Yeah, it took some time for people to accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.52,0:05:26.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 我猜也是\N{\fs38}Yeah, I bet. I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.12,0:05:28.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊有点像手机\N{\fs38}Yeah, it's kind of like cellphones, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.84,0:05:30.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一开始 大家都 \N{\fs38}At first, everyone was like,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.24,0:05:31.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"看那几个傻逼在那搞清除"\N{\fs38}"Look at those douchebags purging,"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.88,0:05:32.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后就变成了\N{\fs38}And then the next thing you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.94,0:05:34.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"这真方便啊"\N{\fs38}They're like, "It's just so convenient."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.62,0:05:36.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天呐 Morty你这是在为了喜剧俱乐部\N{\fs38}Geez, you working on your tight five
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.34,0:05:37.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备单口相声么\N{\fs38}For the comedy store, Morty?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.02,0:05:42.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干什么呢\N{\fs38}Whatcha doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.98,0:05:45.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看电视 玩手机吗\N{\fs38}Watching some TV, playing on your phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.46,0:05:48.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你是认真在问我  - 就是想聊聊天\N{\fs38}- Is that a real question? - Just making conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.44,0:05:51.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是么 你说的哪句话让我能接着聊下去啊\N{\fs38}Are you? What part of that gives me anything to work with?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.34,0:05:54.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的选择要么是不作回答 要么冷嘲热讽\N{\fs38}My choice is to say nothing, be sarcastic,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.20,0:05:55.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者喊一句 "是啊" 就像个训练过的动物一样\N{\fs38}Or bark "Yes" Like a trained animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.06,0:05:57.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也不能算对话\N{\fs38}It's not a conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.54,0:05:59.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是语言绑架我啊\N{\fs38}You're holding me verbally hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.22,0:06:01.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 混蛋 我去厨房了\N{\fs38}Okay, ass-face. I'll go in the kitchen.
