Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:04.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干什么呢 进厨房吗\N{\fs38}Whatcha doing? Going into the kitchen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.86,0:06:05.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs38}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.56,0:06:07.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 是么 你喜欢这样  - 去你的\N{\fs38}- Yeah, you like that?  - Screw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.06,0:06:12.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 大多数人清除的时候都戴面具么\N{\fs38}So, uh, do most people wear masks when they purge?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.38,0:06:14.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我不想再回答任何关于清除的问题了\N{\fs38}I-I don't want to answer any more purge questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.16,0:06:15.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 没事的\N{\fs38}All right, hey, hey, that's cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.00,0:06:17.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没关系的\N{\fs38}I can roll with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.38,0:06:25.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我的外婆  - 哈\N{\fs38}- My nana! - Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.72,0:06:27.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我外婆 我们得救她\N{\fs38}My nana! We have to save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:31.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚想起来你外婆还在呢\N{\fs38}You just now remembered your nana exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.06,0:06:34.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我受到了心理创伤\N{\fs38}I-I was traumatized.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.10,0:06:36.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你大概经历过15次大清除了吧\N{\fs38}Haven't you been through like 15 purges?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.34,0:06:37.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些小时候就经历了\N{\fs38}I mean, some as a child?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.40,0:06:39.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人能帮我救救她吗\N{\fs38}Will somebody just help me get her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.18,0:06:41.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 随便 Morty 留下\N{\fs38}Fine, whatever. Morty, stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.36,0:06:52.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦天呐 哦我靠 我靠\N{\fs38}Oh, god. Oh, crap. Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.34,0:06:55.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 滚出来 滚出来  - 嘿 喔 喔 喔\N{\fs38}- Get out! Get out! - Hey, whoa, whoa, whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.12,0:06:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[哔]滚出那个飞行机器\N{\fs38}Get the [bleep] out of the flying machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.36,0:06:58.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦我的天呐 好 好的 好的\N{\fs38}Oh, my god! O-okay! Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.96,0:07:00.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 退后 混蛋  - 啊啊啊\N{\fs38}- back up, asshole. - Ahh
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.56,0:07:02.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 退后  - 哦\N{\fs38}- Back up.  - Ohh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.24,0:07:03.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- [哔]退后点  - 啊\N{\fs38}- Back the up!  - Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.94,0:07:07.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这么说有用的话 我很抱歉\N{\fs38}For what it's worth, I'm sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.62,0:07:09.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但今晚说什么都没有用\N{\fs38}But that's not really worth anything tonight, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.39,0:07:12.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 你不能把我们扔在这 你这是在谋杀我们\N{\fs38}Y-you can't leave us here. You're killing us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.92,0:07:14.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听到了么 回来\N{\fs38}You hear me? Come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.00,0:07:17.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 你得回来 快改变你的主意\N{\fs38}Y-you got to come back. Change your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.86,0:07:20.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 天呐\N{\fs38}Oh, geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.48,0:07:23.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty 啊 那个[哔]阿米什婊子射了我\N{\fs38}Morty! Aah! The [bleep] Amish bitch shot me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.48,0:07:23.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,\N{\fs38\an8}阿米什人 美国北美宗教社群 拒绝现代设施 过着简朴的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.84,0:07:25.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她想清除我 Morty\N{\fs38}She tried to purge me, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.38,0:07:27.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟着自己的小弟弟走 现在我要死了\N{\fs38}You let your wiener do the walking, and now I'm dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.24,0:07:29.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Rick 她把车给抢了  - 你[哔]逗我呢 Morty\N{\fs38}- Rick, she took the car!  - You [bleep] kidding me, Morty?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.65,0:07:31.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她把我的枪和车都抢走了\N{\fs38}She took my car and the gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.15,0:07:32.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在跟这群混球没区别了\N{\fs38}We're like the rest of these assholes now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.67,0:07:34.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我们要被他们屠了\N{\fs38}W- w- we're gonna get purged, Morty.
