Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.31,0:07:36.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老天 要命了\N{\fs38}Oh, geez, geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:37.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 Rick\N{\fs38}Wait a minute, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.38,0:07:38.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不用你的传送枪\N{\fs38}Why don't we just use your portal gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.66,0:07:40.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在飞船里 蠢货\N{\fs38}It's in the car, dip-ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.08,0:07:41.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疼死我了\N{\fs38}Oh, god, it hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.46,0:07:43.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她正好射中我的肝\N{\fs38}She got me right in the goddamn liver, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.14,0:07:45.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是银河系最辛勤工作的肝了\N{\fs38}It's the hardest-working liver in the galaxy, Morty,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.24,0:07:47.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在上面破了个洞 希望这血没白流\N{\fs38}And now it has a hole in it. I hope it was worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.66,0:07:48.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想做对的事\N{\fs38}I was just trying to do right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.86,0:07:50.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可不是今晚狂欢的主题\N{\fs38}Yeah, well, that's not really the theme of tonight's party.
