Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.98,0:07:57.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难不成我上 我拿肝上的窟窿套他们吗\N{\fs38}No, me. Should I rub my liver hole on them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.16,0:07:58.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捡根棍子什么的敲死他们\N{\fs38}Pick up a stick or something and kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.90,0:08:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 我们为和平而来\N{\fs38}Um, w- we come in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.14,0:08:02.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是扶不上墙\N{\fs38}Oh, my god.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.55,0:08:06.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那玩意我还多的是\N{\fs38}There's more where that came from!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.81,0:08:08.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们想被清除掉吗 放马过来\N{\fs38}You want to get purged, you bring it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.26,0:08:10.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把家伙放下 全都放下\N{\fs38}Drop, drop your shit! Drop it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.50,0:08:12.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty 把他们的家伙抄了 赶紧\N{\fs38}Morty, go get their shit. Hurry up.
