Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.72,0:08:21.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 要吃饼干吗  - 不要吃\N{\fs38}- Want some crackers? - No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:23.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么时候能对我态度好起来\N{\fs38}Are you ready to be nice to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.33,0:08:25.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了区区一盒饼干吗\N{\fs38}In exchange for crackers?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.17,0:08:26.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底怎么了\N{\fs38}What happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.33,0:08:27.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧找个工作吧 老爸\N{\fs38}Dad, get a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.93,0:08:30.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的生活太无聊了 才在这里找事\N{\fs38}You're trying to create drama because you're bored.
