Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.22,0:08:36.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 喂  - Summer 我是外公\N{\fs38}- Hello? - Hey, Summer, it's grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.02,0:08:38.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得帮我个忙\N{\fs38}I need you to do me a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.48,0:08:40.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我听不清楚  - 谁啊\N{\fs38}- I can barely hear you. - Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.03,0:08:41.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟Morty在一个正在搞大清除的星球\N{\fs38}Morty and I are on a planet that's purging.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.83,0:08:44.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你要记下  - 什么锡球\N{\fs38}- I need you to take down... - A plan that's what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.03,0:08:46.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在一个正在大清除的星球 大清除\N{\fs38}We're on a planet that's purging, Summer. Purging.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.28,0:08:48.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的飞船和枪都被抢走了 我们正在一场大清除中\N{\fs38}We lost our car and my gun, and we're in a purge.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.46,0:08:49.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是Taddi Mason打来的吗\N{\fs38}Ooh, is it Taddi Mason?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.69,0:08:51.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像那部电影一样吗\N{\fs38}Like the movie "The purge"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.18,0:08:52.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 你得记\N{\fs38}Yes, I- I need you to take...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.33,0:08:53.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那部电影烂透了\N{\fs38}That movie sucked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.47,0:08:55.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天呐 等一下\N{\fs38}Oh, my god. Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:56.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是Taddi Mason吗\N{\fs38}It's not Taddi Mason?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.38,0:08:58.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爸 Taddi Mason[哔]是谁\N{\fs38}Dad, who the [bleep] is Taddi Mason?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.37,0:08:59.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 一个朋友  - 啊\N{\fs38}- My friend. - Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.22,0:09:01.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吗 我开免提了\N{\fs38}Are you okay? I'm putting you on speaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.23,0:09:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Taddi吗  - 是啊Jerry 我是Taddi\N{\fs38}- Taddi? - Yes, Jerry, it's Taddi,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.08,0:09:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前从来没人听说过的人\N{\fs38}A person no one's ever heard of until now,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.73,0:09:06.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在正拿太空电话打给你呢\N{\fs38}Calling you on a space phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.22,0:09:07.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我分不出你是不是在讽刺\N{\fs38}I can't tell if you're being sarcastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.82,0:09:14.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,装弹 赶快\N{\fs38}Reload, fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.03,0:09:17.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Summer 你得记下这串数字\N{\fs38}Summer, w- we need you to take down this number.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.16,0:09:19.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 别扯别的  - Morty吗 你没事吧\N{\fs38}- Quit screwing around. - Morty? Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.53,0:09:21.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 当然有事  - 你怎么和Taddi Mason在一起\N{\fs38}- No! - Why are you with Taddi Mason?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.78,0:09:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我[哔] 你[哔]闭嘴吧老爸\N{\fs38}Holy [bleep] Dad! Shut the [bleep] up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.89,0:09:27.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧看来 我就是全家人的出气筒\N{\fs38}Okay. I guess I'm just this entire family's toilet paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.08,0:09:29.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有在记吗 快把数字记下来\N{\fs38}Are you writing this down? Will you please write this down?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.33,0:09:32.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 好好  - 7 7 1 9 8\N{\fs38}- Yes, yes. - 7, 7, 1, 9, 8...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.92,0:09:37.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3 6 4 2 1 1 2 5\N{\fs38}3, 6, 4, 2, 1, 1, 2, 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.37,0:09:43.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这狗日的\N{\fs38}You son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.00,0:09:45.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty 我也不想求助\N{\fs38}Morty, I don't want to be the "A little help" Guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.98,0:09:47.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你能搭把手吗\N{\fs38}But a little help?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.60,0:09:50.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 我找到笔了 说\N{\fs38}Okay, I have a pen. Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.75,0:09:54.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,7 7 1 9 8 3 6 4 2 1 1 2 5\N{\fs38}7, 7, 1, 9, 8, 3, 6, 4, 2, 1, 1, 2, 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.90,0:09:55.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就给我个勺子吗\N{\fs38}A spoon, Morty?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.66,0:09:57.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你搞什么  - 对不起\N{\fs38}- A spoon?! - I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.13,0:09:58.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你旁边这么多餐具\N{\fs38}There's a pile of silverware next to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.72,0:10:01.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我个最没杀伤力的东西\N{\fs38}And you throw me the one thing that can never kill anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.33,0:10:02.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我错了还不行吗\N{\fs38}All right, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.33,0:10:05.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,车库里我工作台上有个架子\N{\fs38}Summer, on the shelf above my workbench in the garage,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.16,0:10:07.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一个带键盘的红盒子\N{\fs38}There's a red box with a keypad on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.12,0:10:08.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把盒子拿到外面\N{\fs38}You're gonna take that box outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.58,0:10:10.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,输入我刚才给你报的数字\N{\fs38}and you're gonna type the number I just gave you into the keypad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.69,0:10:11.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 明白吗  - 明白\N{\fs38}- Got it? - Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.74,0:10:14.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恨自己的老爸是成长的一部分吗\N{\fs38}Is it just part of growing up to hate your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.23,0:10:15.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,懒得搭理你\N{\fs38}I'm ignoring you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.42,0:10:18.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我能到那个灯塔顶上\N{\fs38}Morty, if I can get to the top of that lighthouse,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.45,0:10:20.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就可以发射信标 你姐就能把东西送过来\N{\fs38}I can send the beacon, and your sister can launch our package.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.80,0:10:22.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记住了 如果那里有人\N{\fs38}Just remember, if there's people in there
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.41,0:10:24.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且他们想杀我们的话 我们先把他们弄死\N{\fs38}And they try to purge us, we got to purge them first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.49,0:10:27.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们谁也不弄死 Rick 能不能别这样\N{\fs38}We're not purging anyone, Rick, all right? W- will you stop it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.28,0:10:28.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果还想看见明天的太阳\N{\fs38}Morty, if we're gonna survive tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.63,0:10:30.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得学会驾驭你压抑的愤怒\N{\fs38}You're gonna need to harness your repressed rage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.50,0:10:31.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有压抑的愤怒\N{\fs38}I don't have any!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.33,0:10:33.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这语气就挺压抑的\N{\fs38}Spoken like a person with repressed rage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.17,0:10:39.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有参加节日\N{\fs38}I take no part in the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.76,0:10:41.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你们想杀我 只求下手麻利点\N{\fs38}If you desire to kill me, I only ask you do it quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.96,0:10:43.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没这个打算\N{\fs38}No such agenda, chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.26,0:10:45.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们对大清除也没什么兴趣\N{\fs38}We're not too keen on the purge, either, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.31,0:10:47.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只想到你灯塔顶上\N{\fs38}We were just hoping to get on the roof of your lighthouse
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.33,0:10:49.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为我在地球的姐姐设一个信标\N{\fs38}So we can send a beacon to my sister on earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.39,0:10:50.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 那是另外一个星球  - 顺便说一句\N{\fs38}- It's a different planet. - By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.99,0:10:53.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别的星球也存在生命 不过重点不在这儿\N{\fs38}Life on other planets exists. Don't let it distract you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.43,0:10:56.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们可以藏在我的灯塔里 设信标\N{\fs38}I'll let you use my lighthouse for shelter and beacon-sending
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.09,0:10:57.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过条件是 你们得听听我写的故事剧本\N{\fs38}On the condition that you listen to my tale.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.80,0:10:58.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 好  - 成交\N{\fs38}- Okay. - Deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.88,0:11:00.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去楼顶把东西弄好\N{\fs38}All right, I'm gonna go to the roof and set things up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:03.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Morty 你听他读  - 好\N{\fs38}- Morty, you listen to his tale. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.00,0:11:14.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"镜头淡入 外景 不知名的城市 白天"\N{\fs38}"Fade in. Exterior. Unnamed city. Day."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.07,0:11:16.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"进步的路上 熙熙攘攘"\N{\fs38}"The hustle and bustle is a symphony of progress."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.08,0:11:18.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"镜头略过形形色色的窗户 每扇中都是一个故事"\N{\fs38}"We pan past windows, each of which contain a different story,"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.79,0:11:19.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"最终定格在Jacey Lakims身上"\N{\fs38}"To find Jacey Lakims,"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.93,0:11:21.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"这个年方二八的惹火少妇丝毫没有意识到自己的美丽"\N{\fs38}"28, hot, but doesn't know it."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.83,0:11:23.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"Jacey不得不停了下来"\N{\fs38}"Jacey stops when her high heel gets caught"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.45,0:11:24.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"因为高跟鞋卡在了下水道格栅里"\N{\fs38}"In the grating of a sewer."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:27.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"突然一个男人出现 用枪指着她"\N{\fs38}"Suddenly, a man steps into frame and points a gun at her."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.66,0:11:29.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"她今天不走运"\N{\fs38}"This is not her day."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.07,0:11:31.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"镜头淡入黑暗"\N{\fs38}"Fade to black."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.47,0:11:34.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,几个字浮现 "三周前"\N{\fs38}Title--'three weeks earlier'.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.29,0:11:39.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的不想谈谈吗\N{\fs38}You really don't want to talk to me about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.13,0:11:41.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爸 外公和Morty情况危险\N{\fs38}Dad, grandpa and Morty are in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.44,0:11:43.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你 正失业中 只是无聊\N{\fs38}You're unemployed, and you're bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.26,0:11:45.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 孰轻孰重自有分晓  - 别再说失业的事好吗\N{\fs38}- They're a higher priority. - Stop saying I'm unemployed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.89,0:11:50.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,7 7 1 9 8 3 6 4 2 1 1 2 5\N{\fs38}Okay, 7, 7, 1, 9, 8, 3, 6, 4, 2, 1, 1, 2, 5
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.23,0:11:50.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事\N{\fs38}Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:52.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这什么东西 又闹哪出\N{\fs38}Good lord! Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.22,0:11:57.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着 我是你的父亲 我只是想说 我是爱你的\N{\fs38}Look, I'm your father, and I love you is all I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.38,0:11:59.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 仅此而已  - 说完你就满意了吧\N{\fs38}- I'll leave it at that. - Fine, dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.27,0:12:04.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外公好像说过要先拿到外面去\N{\fs38}Oh, he might have said to take it outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.30,0:12:05.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点啊 Summer\N{\fs38}Come on, Summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.11,0:12:07.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往盒子上输几个数字有什么难的\N{\fs38}How hard is it to type some numbers into a box?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.53,0:12:09.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标锁定\N{\fs38}Target locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.23,0:12:10.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢天谢地\N{\fs38}Oh, thank god.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.58,0:12:13.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟Summer这边都万事俱备\N{\fs38}Well, I did my job. Summer did her job.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.45,0:12:16.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只欠Morty听完他的剧本了\N{\fs38}Now all Morty has to do is finish listening to that tale.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.32,0:12:19.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Blaine说"可能我不需要新朋友"\N{\fs38}Blaine: Maybe I don't need a new friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.48,0:12:21.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jacey说"可能你是我唯一需要的朋友"\N{\fs38}Jacey: Maybe you're the only friend I need.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.96,0:12:24.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Blaine说"需要还是想要"\N{\fs38}Blaine: Need, or want?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.18,0:12:26.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jacey说"我从未如此渴望过"\N{\fs38}Jacey: I've never been much for wanting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.59,0:12:28.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Blaine "这语气像是有迫切需求的人"\N{\fs38}Blaine: Spoken like someone with needs."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.86,0:12:30.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 老天爷  - 什么\N{\fs38}- Oh, geez. - Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.06,0:12:31.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 请 请继续\N{\fs38}Uh, sorry. K-keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.06,0:12:34.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"Jacey伸手拂过他的脸颊"\N{\fs38}"Jacey reaches out and touches his face."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.02,0:12:35.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"很明显他所需正是她所想"\N{\fs38}"It's clear he needs what she wants."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.64,0:12:36.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"男女相遇 干柴烈火"\N{\fs38}"She's a woman. He's a man."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.98,0:12:39.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"他将她揽入怀中 城市废墟在身后熊熊燃烧"\N{\fs38}"The city burns in the background as he takes her in his arms."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:40.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"镜头淡出"\N{\fs38}"Fade out."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.17,0:12:42.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,几个字浮现 "剧终"\N{\fs38}Title--'The End'.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.20,0:12:44.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"再加个问号"\N{\fs38}"Question mark."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.08,0:12:45.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 哇  - 可以吧\N{\fs38}- Wow. - Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.63,0:12:48.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这真是 不错 写得好\N{\fs38}It's...g-good job. Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.43,0:12:50.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你喜欢吗  - 当然喜欢\N{\fs38}- You liked it? - Of course I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.13,0:12:51.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酒吧那部分你没有笑\N{\fs38}You didn't laugh at the scene in the bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.46,0:12:55.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那段挺搞笑的 但是我想听后面的部分\N{\fs38}I...thought it was funny, but I wanted to hear the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.13,0:12:56.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么想法吗 意见呢\N{\fs38}Do you have any thoughts? Notes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.94,0:12:59.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有 仅仅是乐在其中\N{\fs38}No. I-I just enjoyed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.08,0:13:01.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我的意见 请再多写一点\N{\fs38}That's my note, you know? Please write more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.33,0:13:03.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 感觉你在敷衍  - 不不\N{\fs38}- Seems a little insincere. - What? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.36,0:13:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用好言哄我\N{\fs38}You don't have to mollycoddle me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.72,0:13:07.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想改进我的写作 说出你的真实想法\N{\fs38}I want to improve my writing. Tell me your real thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.08,0:13:10.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 呃 从我个人角度来说\N{\fs38}All right. Well, um, I'm not a huge fan, personally,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.46,0:13:12.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是很喜欢那个"三周前"开场戏的倒叙\N{\fs38}Of the whole "Three weeks earlier" teaser thing.
